        public void setEmptyDateAttributes(java.lang.String value)
        Optional RegEx of attributes to convert to dates; if the value of the attribute is empty, it is left empty. This regex takes precedence over both this.currentDateDateAttributes and this.dateAttributes, i.e. if an attribute matches both this.emptyDateAttributes and this.dateAttributes, the default value for an empty attribute will be an empty date

      • setCurrentDateDateAttributes

        public void setCurrentDateDateAttributes(java.lang.String value)
        Optional RegEx of attributes to convert to dates; if the value of the attribute is empty, it is set to the current date. This regex takes precedence over this.dateAttributes, i.e. if an attribute matches both this.currentDateDateAttributes and this.dateAttributes, the default value for an empty attribute will be the current date
